trans-unit.resname: Following my studies (DUT Biological Engineering, Bachelor and Master in Computer Science, specialization in Bioinformatics), I decided to enter the world of work by creating my bioinformatics services company BILMS (Bioinformatics, Computer Science, Software, Maintenance, Services), in order to provide biology research laboratories with an external service, putting at my disposal my know-how and my expertise acquired throughout my studies.
trans-unit.source: Following my studies (DUT Biological Engineering, Bachelor and Master in Computer Science, specialization in Bioinformatics), I decided to enter the world of work by creating my bioinformatics services company BILMS (Bioinformatics, Computer Science, Software, Maintenance, Services), in order to provide biology research laboratories with an external service, putting at my disposal my know-how and my expertise acquired throughout my studies.
trans-unit.target: Suite à mes études (DUT Génie Biologique, Licence et Master en Informatique, spécialisation en Bioinformatique), j'ai décidé d'entrer dans le monde du travail en créant une entreprise de bioinformatique, BILMS (Bioinformatique, Informatique, Logiciels, Maintenance, Services), afin de fournir des services externalisés de bioinformatique à des laboratoires de recherche, mettant à disposition mon savoir-faire et mon expertise acquis tout au long de mes études.

trans-unit.resname: Sometimes the perspectives of each changes, that's why I considered a less administrative job, more focused on my technical skills. With this in mind, I gladly put my skills at Synap System, an open source solutions consulting company, for nearly a year and a half. Then came a mission to Acretion to participate in the development of an intelligent social network dedicated to sharing values, via an innovative strategy.
trans-unit.source: Sometimes the perspectives of each changes, that's why I considered a less administrative job, more focused on my technical skills. With this in mind, I gladly put my skills at Synap System, an open source solutions consulting company, for nearly a year and a half. Then came a mission to Acretion to participate in the development of an intelligent social network dedicated to sharing values, via an innovative strategy.
trans-unit.target: Parfois les perspectives de chacun changent, c'est pourquoi j'ai envisagé un travail moins administratif, davantage axé sur mes compétences techniques. Dans cette optique, j'ai mis avec plaisir mes compétences en oeuvre chez Synap System, société de conseil en solutions open source, pendant près d'un an et demi. Puis s'en est suivi une mission pour Acretion en participant au développement d'un réseau social intelligent dédié au partage de valeurs, via une stratégie innovante.
